Class InlineBoxMeasurements

java.lang.Object
  org.xhtmlrenderer.layout.InlineBoxMeasurements

public class InlineBoxMeasurements
extends java.lang.Object

A bean which tracks various charactistics of an inline box. It is used when calculating the vertical position of boxes in a line.
